Clean Compression (repo-ready)

Fix the Cup:
Map leaks → seal them → add containment → control flow → stress test → scale input only after retention stabilizes.

Agents: Gremlins (leaks), Wardens (containment), Alchemists (compression), Echoes (reactivation).

Invariant: Retention ≥ Input.

